      "span_text": "Mission Analysis, VASCOMP Here, the fuel weight required to perform a representative EUROFAR-mission 9 (Figure 2) is calculated, and it is checked if the aircraft power available (EUROFARbaseline [CITATION_1] ) is sufficient to hover out of ground effect (HOGE) at 500m ISA +10°, with full mission fuel and payload (equivalent to design gross weight)."
